                "lines": "817",
                "category": "pragmatic/stale-comment",
                "diagnosis": "Comment says 'Helper function defined in cargo_test.go but we need it here too.' containsSubstr has exactly one definition (here in go_test.go); cargo_test.go has no such function. repair_loop_test.go already has a corrected note pointing to go_test.go. Delete or fix the comment."
