              }
            ],
            "summary": "One blocking issue: discoverBinariesFromProxy duplicates downloadArtifact without a comment explaining the deliberate divergence, creating a silent maintenance trap. Two advisory issues: stale comment attributing containsSubstr to cargo_test.go (it only exists in go_test.go), and a test-only constructor that is exported unnecessarily. Core logic of the ZIP scanning, fallback strategy, size limits, and BinaryNameProvider exclusion is sound."
